<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — PackersHub" description="How PackersHub collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you request a quote or book a move." noindex={true} breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Home', url: '/' }, { name: 'Privacy Policy', url: '/privacy/' }]}>
  <section class="bg-hero py-16"><div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 text-center"><h1 class="display-lg text-slate-900 font-display font-black">Privacy Policy</h1></div></section>
  <section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 prose prose-lg prose-headings:font-display">
    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 2026</p>
    <p>This Privacy Policy explains how PackersHub ("we", "us") collects, uses, stores, and protects your personal information when you visit our website, request a quote, or book our packers and movers services. This is a general template and not a substitute for legal advice — PackersHub should have this reviewed by a qualified lawyer for full compliance with India's Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023 and other applicable law.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you contact PackersHub via phone, WhatsApp, our website forms, or our chat assistant, we may collect: your name, phone number, email address (if provided), pickup and destination addresses, move date, and details about the items being moved. We do not knowingly collect sensitive personal data (such as financial account details, health information, or government ID numbers) through our website forms.</p>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your contact details to: respond to enquiries and provide quotations; schedule and coordinate your move; send booking confirmations and service updates; and improve our services. We do not sell your personal information to third parties, and we do not use it for unrelated marketing without your consent.</p>

    <h2>3. WhatsApp and Chat Assistant</h2>
    <p>If you contact us via WhatsApp or use the AI chat assistant on our website, your message content is used to respond to your query and, where applicable, processed by our messaging or AI service providers solely to generate that response. We retain conversation records only as long as needed to handle your enquiry or booking, and for a reasonable period afterward for service-quality and dispute-resolution purposes.</p>

    <h2>4. Cookies and Website Analytics</h2>
    <p>Our website may use basic, privacy-respecting analytics to understand how visitors use our pages (for example, which city pages are most viewed). We do not use this data to identify individual visitors personally.</p>

    <h2>5. Information Sharing</h2>
    <p>We share your information only with: our own moving crew and logistics partners, strictly to plan and execute your booking; payment processors, to complete transactions; and law enforcement or regulators, only if legally required. We do not share your data with advertisers or unrelated third parties.</p>

    <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain booking and contact information for as long as necessary to provide our services, comply with legal/tax obligations, and resolve any disputes — typically no longer than is reasonably required for these purposes.</p>

    <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal information held by PackersHub by contacting us using the details below. We will respond to verified requests within a reasonable timeframe.</p>

    <h2>8. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We take reasonable technical and organisational measures to protect your information from unauthorised access, loss, or misuse. No method of transmission or storage is 100% secure, but we work to protect your data to industry-reasonable standards.</p>

    <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available at this page, with the "Last Updated" date revised accordingly.</p>

    <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related questions or requests, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@packershub.in">info@packershub.in</a> or call <a href="tel:+917731074075">+91 77310 74075</a>. Registered office: BV Nagar, Nellore, Andhra Pradesh, India — 524004.</p>
  </div></section>
